Simple Note Pad Project Progress


Weeks 1 to 3 Foundation and Structure

Project Initiation: Defined the core purpose of Simple Note Pad as a lightweight productivity tool.

Architecture: Set up the Android Studio project environment and established the basic activity hierarchy.

Navigation: Implemented the first Intent to link the main dashboard with the note creation screen.

UI Framing: Drafted initial XML layouts and explored Material3 design principles.


Week 4 Implementation and Interaction Current

Functional Editor: Fully developed the EditNoteActivity with input fields for titles and content.

User Feedback: Added Toast notifications to provide immediate validation when saving notes.

Theme Styling: Applied NoActionBar and customized color schemes to enhance readability.

Code Refinement: Cleaned up Java logic to ensure robust input validation preventing empty notes.
